{"tid":699300,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解本絲打咁靚女 都要比人呃感情","createTime":"2018-06-12T11:48:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T00:39:03.000Z","uid":18535,"like":1,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"70a639a64bf4e21b42343d175c751c4c26e92b74","tid":699300,"uid":18535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:48:56.000Z","msg":"日前係連登識咗個有錢巴打<br />\n雖然我唔貪錢 <br />\n但諗在佢第一次見就買個hermes包包比本絲打咁有心思 就同佢一齊咗<br />\n一個星期後佢話出trip 我話想跟埋佢佢又唔比<br />\n咁我就起疑心啦 立即打開佢部電腦<br />\n點知真係比我發現到佢真係呃住我<br />\n<br />\n個hermes原來係淘寶買返黎嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我當即時打電話同佢對質<br />\n但佢仲不斷拉開話題講自已一個去 無對我唔住<br />\n本絲打最憎呢種唔知我點諗既男仔<br />\n其實我真係唔在意個袋 但點解要呃我呀<br />\n呢種講大話又唔細心既男仔真係唔要得<br />\n我即時飛咗佢 頭也不回<br />\n<br />\n點解 點解本絲打咁靚 <br />\n但成日都會遇到呢D賤男<br />\n有無姊妹黎評評理"},{"pid":"d9b6f8de4534c9a062eefdeeb4ec3d18d8eb63b7","tid":699300,"uid":168525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:50:28.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"8490390b62892b03f56bfef087eb05f8b24f238d","tid":699300,"uid":148185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c17c465637db8f8c62eb137b7733426cf54515","tid":699300,"uid":5674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:51:42.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"08c9080ed9127c824246d0943dcde0a9e53ae299","tid":699300,"uid":21423,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:51:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67ee8fc7610f8827f778e6130f82603b5f4ebeac","tid":699300,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:52:12.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"a3721edcec1b243600e70234eb8fef0c1101ed37","tid":699300,"uid":64847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:53:32.000Z","msg":"好人好者點會上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" 